snippet: At least 24 people were killed and seven injured when the roof of a mosque in the eastern city of Lahore collapsed Tuesday.
abstract: Roof of mosque in Lahore, Pakistan, collapses, killing at least 24 people and injuring seven others.
lead_paragraph: At least 24 people were killed and seven injured when the roof of a mosque in the eastern city of Lahore collapsed Tuesday.

headline.main: Pakistan: 24 Killed When Mosque Roof Collapses
headline.print_headline: Pakistan: 24 Killed When Mosque Roof Collapses
